snippet.title: GAR-TYPE: Launch Trailer (Gorefield Fangame)
snippet.description:
You're our last hope, Jon. Save the Earth! Play the game now for free:
itch.io link (downloadable version is here): https://lumpytouch.itch.io/gar-type
Newgrounds link: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/961445

GORESTAR, the living planet, is on a direct course for Earth.
It's time to debut our secret weapon duo:
Ace pilot Jon Starbuckle, and his prototype starfighter, Gar-Type D.
Your mission: save humanity! Defend the Earth from the alien invaders!

GAR-TYPE credits:
Art + Sound Effects: LumpyTouch

Programming: qkjosh
https://sparrowhousegames.itch.io/

Music: MelonadeM
https://melonadem.com/

Monday Mode battle theme: psychoangel
https://www.youtube.com/@psycho_angel

Gar-Type D 3D model: willkmr
https://www.instagram.com/willkmr/?hl=en

Monday Mode game over music: stevedoesmusic
https://soundcloud.com/stevedoesmusic

Special thanks to my Patreon Pals who support my creations and help me make fun stuff like this! https://www.patreon.com/LumpyTouch

Trailer music: Blue Revolver OST - Aerolith Aurorablast 
Composed by: Qygen https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fh3Fiq2F3mE

#fangame #animation #gaming #garfield #pixelart
